canonical:
  title: 赤道寺
  author: 金富軾
  language: lzh
  text: 聖祖樓船憇此中江山王氣尙葱葱當時故事無人識除却堂堂十八公
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 赤道寺
  author: 金富軾
  language: lzh
  text: 聖祖樓船憇此中。江山王氣尙葱葱。當時故事無人識。除却堂堂十八公。
korean:
  title: 적도사
  author: 김부식
  language: kor
  text: |-
    성조의 누선이 이곳에서 쉬었거니
    강산의 왕기는 아직도 자욱하다
    당당한 십팔공(十八公) 제해 놓고는
    그때의 고사를 아는 이 없네
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0220_020_0270&viewSync=OT
  footnotes:
  - key: '[주-D001] 십팔공(十八公) : '
    value: 솔[松]을 십팔공(十八公)이라 하는데, 송(松) 자를 파자(破字)한 것이다.
english:
  title: The Red Path Temple
  author: Kim Bu-sik
  language: eng
  text: |-
    The Sacred Ancestor's river-boat found rest within these walls,
    And still the mountain's imperial fortune rises thick as mist.
    But who remembers now the tales of those ancient days?
    Save only for the Eighteen Sages standing proud and tall.
  footnotes:
    - The 'Eighteen Sages' (十八公) refers to pine trees, a play on the character 松 (pine), which when broken down resembles the number eighteen written in classical form.
